N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 692.3 - College and law school certificates

State Regulations
A certificate shall be submitted from
each college and law school attended by the applicant, setting forth the
information required by forms which shall be provided to the applicant for that
purpose. Notes
